OL,7,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Malcolm Shaw has
OL,8,Fbeen following the trial at Brighton
OL,9,FCrown Court.
OL,11,FA 16-year-old boy has been found
OL,12,Fguilty of murder after a teenager was
OL,13,Fstabbed in broad daylight in Brighton.
OL,15,FThe teenager from Southwick, who can't
OL,16,Fbe named for legal reasons, was found
OL,17,Funanimously guilty following a trial
OL,18,Fat Brighton Crown Court.
OL,20,FHe will be sentenced at a later date.
