OL,7,FMustafa Momand's parents previously
OL,8,Ftold the court of their efforts to
OL,9,Fsave him from his drug dealing and
OL,10,Fshared drug debt of #20,000.
OL,12,FBefore his death, his mother Suraya
OL,13,FMomand said he told her he "regretted
OL,14,Feverything" and talked about going to
OL,15,Fcollege to study law to help exploited
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,FDuring the trial, Mustafa's parents
OL,19,Frevealed how they "begged" police to
OL,20,Fsend their 17-year-old son to prison
OL,21,Fto get him away from drug dealing.
