OL,7,FJurors had heard when Mustafa turned
OL,8,F16, things "got worse" and his
OL,9,Fbehaviour changed, his parents found
OL,10,Fweapons in his pockets and he went
OL,11,Fmissing for days on occasion, coming
OL,12,Fback with valuable items or injuries.
OL,14,FJurors heard how Mustafa had moved to
OL,15,Fthe UK from Afghanistan with his
OL,16,Ffamily in 2009 when he was three years
OL,17,Fold, and in late 2021 his mother found
OL,18,Fcannabis in his room and suspected he
OL,19,Fwas using or dealing drugs.
