OL,7,FIn a statement read aloud to court,
OL,8,FMustafa's father, Noor Momand, said he
OL,9,Ffirst became worried when his son came
OL,10,Fhome very late on his 16th birthday
OL,11,Fdespite his family waiting with a
OL,12,Fbirthday cake for him.
OL,14,FWhen he did come home he had with him
OL,15,Fa "very expensive" bottle of Chanel
OL,16,Fperfume, which he said a friend gave
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,19,F"I was worried he was being exploited
OL,20,Fin some way," Mr Momand said.
