OL,7,FThe court heard how Mustafa was housed
OL,8,Fby social services in Bevendean, in
OL,9,FBrighton in early 2023, because his
OL,10,Fmother felt she could not look after
OL,11,Fhim at home any more.
OL,13,FHe was later moved out of the area to
OL,14,FCroydon, south London, where he
OL,15,Fregistered to attend college for a two-
OL,16,Fyear A-Level Business and Law course
OL,17,Ffor September 2023.
